.org\/wiki\"\/Nelson_Mandela\" title=\"Nelson Mandela\">Nelson Mandela<\/a> of Asia\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-reconcilation_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"https:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Kim_Dae-jung#\"cite_note-reconcilation-3\">[3]<\/a><\/sup> Kim was the first opposition candidate to win the presidency.\n<\/p>","bio_image":"full\/ed9f1de5d92e3417c1ac415f7f2a096bed0c3063.jpg"}]